window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ellen Ripley awakens onboard the space station <i>Auriga</i>. Her last memory is of her own fiery death. And yet she is somehow alive. </p> <p>Ripley discovers that her \"resurrection\" is a result of an incredible experiment that has altered both her and the creature she has been carrying. To combat the incalculable alien menace, she teams up with a renegade band of space smugglers. </p>"; 
